# Stage 8: Battle Defeat Ending

label stage8_ending_battle_defeat:
    scene bg academy_gate with fade

    "The Echo escaped. Wounded but free."

    show h at center with dissolve

    h "The disturbances have decreased, but they haven't stopped."

    "The academy remains unstable. Reality continues to warp in subtle ways."

    show l at left with dissolve

    l "We failed to understand it. Failed to help it."
    l "And now it wanders, causing damage wherever it manifests."

    "You tried force when understanding was needed."
    "The mystery remains unsolved."
    "And somewhere out there, the Echo suffers."

    "Perhaps one day, someone will succeed where you failed."

    $ ending_type = "defeat"

    jump stage8_epilogue_solo
